== Events == * ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} [[1392]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日}}) – {{ill|Yi Seong-gye|ja|李成桂}} founded the 【Yi Dynasty (Joseon)†Joseon】. * {{ill|Kanbun|ja|寛文|12=draft}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1671]] {{ill|May 6|ja|5月6日}}) – The internal conflict within the 【Sendai Domain†Sendai_Domain】, known as the {{ill|Date-sōdō|ja|伊達騒動}}, was resolved by the bakufu. * {{ill|Genroku|ja|元禄}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1689]] {{ill|May 16|ja|5月16日}}) – {{ill|Matsuo Bashō|ja|松尾芭蕉}} departed on his journey to compose 【Oku no Hosomichi|ja:奥の細道】 together with his disciple {{ill|Kawai Sōra|ja|河合曾良}}. * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1854]] {{ill|April 24|ja|4月24日}}) – {{ill|Yoshida Shōin|ja|吉田松陰}} sought passage on an American black ship anchored at Shimoda but was refused. * {{ill|Genji|ja|元治|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1864]] {{ill|May 2|ja|5月2日}}) – The Tengu-dō Rebellion occurred, when the Sonnō jōi faction of the Mito Domain, led by {{ill|Fujita Koshirō|ja|藤田小四郎}}, rose in arms at Mount Tsukuba.
== Births == <!-- (No births listed) -->
