* {{ill|Genroku|ja|元禄|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1689]] {{ill|May 16|ja|5月16日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Matsuo Bashō|ja|松尾芭蕉|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} departed on his journey to compose 【Oku no Hosomichi|ja:奥の細道】 together with his disciple {{ill|Kawai Sōra|ja|河合曾良|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}.
