== Events == * ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1392]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Yi Seong-gye|ja|李成桂|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} founded the 【Yi Dynasty (Joseon)†Joseon】. * {{ill|Kanbun|ja|寛文|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1671]] {{ill|May 6|ja|5月6日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – The internal conflict within the 【Sendai Domain†Sendai_Domain】, known as the {{ill|Date-sōdō|ja|伊達騒動|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, was resolved by the bakufu. * {{ill|Genroku|ja|元禄|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1689]] {{ill|May 16|ja|5月16日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Matsuo Bashō|ja|松尾芭蕉|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} departed on his journey to compose 【Oku no Hosomichi|ja:奥の細道】 together with his disciple {{ill|Kawai Sōra|ja|河合曾良|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1854]] {{ill|April 24|ja|4月24日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Yoshida Shōin|ja|吉田松陰|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} sought passage on an American black ship anchored at Shimoda but was refused. * {{ill|Genji|ja|元治|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1864]] {{ill|May 2|ja|5月2日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – The Tengu-dō Rebellion occurred, when the Sonnō jōi faction of the Mito Domain, led by {{ill|Fujita Koshirō|ja|藤田小四郎|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, rose in arms at Mount Tsukuba.
