== Events == * ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[1392]] [[:en:April 19|April 19]]) – [[:en:Taejo of Joseon|Yi Seong-gye]] founded the 【Yi Dynasty (Joseon)†Joseon】. * [[:en:Kanbun (era)|Kanbun]] 11th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1671]] [[:en:May 6|May 6]]) – The internal conflict within the 【Sendai Domain†Sendai_Domain】, known as the [[:en:Date Sōdō|Date-sōdō]], was resolved by the bakufu. * [[:en:Genroku|Genroku]] 2nd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1689]] [[:en:May 16|May 16]]) – [[:en:Matsuo Bashō|Matsuo Bashō]] departed on his journey to compose 【Oku no Hosomichi|ja:奥の細道】 together with his disciple {{ill|Kawai Sōra|ja|河合曾良|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kawai Sōra|qq=}}. * [[:en:Ansei|Ansei]] 1st year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1854]] [[:en:April 24|April 24]]) – [[:en:Yoshida Shōin|Yoshida Shōin]] sought passage on an American black ship anchored at Shimoda but was refused. * [[:en:Genji era|Genji]] 1st year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1864]] [[:en:May 2|May 2]]) – The Tengu-dō Rebellion occurred, when the Sonnō jōi faction of the Mito Domain, led by {{ill|Fujita Koshirō|ja|藤田小四郎|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fujita Koshirō|qq=}}, rose in arms at Mount Tsukuba.
== Births ==
== Deaths == * [[:en:Eitoku|Eitoku]] 3rd year / [[:en:Kōwa (Muromachi period)|Kōwa]] 3rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[1383]] [[:en:April 30|April 30]]) – [[:en:Prince Kaneyoshi|Naiyoshi Shinnō]], a prince of Emperor Go-Daigo (born [[1329]]).
